 nails, aged skin, and&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">a&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">weaker</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">&nbsp;immune system. That said, studies have found that is why silica holds various health and beauty benefits and</span></p><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">is included as&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit;">one of our Wholy Grail ingredients.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606282518598" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606282518598"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 1.3px;"><strong><br></strong></span></p><p><b><br></b></p><p><b><br></b></p><p><b><i>The Benefits</i>&nbsp;of Horsetail</b></p><p><br></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Tabs" data-key="tabs" id="m-1606282506098" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-tabs" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1606282506098" style=""><div class="gf_restabs module style1 gf_module-left  gf_restabs_accordion_0" data-activetab="1" data-tabbgcolor="#FFFFFF" data-tabcolor="#333333" data-inactivetabbgcolor="#e0e0e0" data-inactivetabcolor="#8d8d8d" data-bordercolor="#cecece" data-bordersize="1px" data-height=""><ul><li class="gf_tab" data-index="1"><span class="item-content" data-index="1" data-key="content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1606282506098-1" class="element-wrap" data-tool="0" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="160